2015-11-09 CHISINAU,Republic of Moldova, Nov. 9, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- After a year of work, Fun Easy Learn has released a major update to their popular Spanish learning app, Learn Spanish 6000 Words. The App now features a redesigned look and much more content to grasp the Spanish language. Logo- http://photos.prnewswire.com/prnh/20151109/285104LOGOPhoto - http://photos.prnewswire.com/prnh/20151109/285105  Fun Easy Learn CEO had this to say about the update to the Learn Spanish 600 Words app.The Spanish language is at an increasing importance for people all over the world. Some of the powerful countries in the world either have Spanish as a national language or have a large Spanish speaking population. This holds true for places like the United States, Spain, Mexico, and some South American countries. To help everyone get a better understanding of the language, Fun Easy Learn has worked tirelessly on creating a Spanish learning app. The latest update to our Learn Spanishapp has seen a total rework of the lessons to the user interface. We are doing everything in our power to make lessons more fun, easy to understand, and fast. We believe that the latest update of the Learn Spanish 6000 Wordsapp has all the key features necessary for new and old users alike to learn better Spanish. We are currently sitting at 5,000,000 downloads of our app in total with more downloads coming as I speak. It is an exciting time for Fun Easy Learn. Learn Spanish 6000 Words update is not all looks, the revamped curriculum will help new users get a grasp of the Spanish language, while also giving people more accustomed to the app new lessons to heighten their skills and proficiency in Spanish. Based out of Republic of Moldova, Fun Easy Learn is a software development company specializing in language apps. The company currently bolsters over 10 different language apps. Users are taught via games, tests, and other challenges that are both entertaining and educational. Users can get a hold of Fun Easy Learn apps by visiting either the Apple App Store or the Google Play Store. If you would like more information about this topic, please contact Andrian at +37369079967 or email. Website: https://www.funeasylearn.com/ To view the original version on PR Newswire, visit:http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/popular-language-app-learn-spanish-6000-words-gets-a-fresh-update-300174736.html SOURCE  Fun Easy Learn 